Rainy day calling for a hot bowl of ramen. @kanadaya.sg  specialized in authentic Tonkotsu Ramen is available for delivery daily from 11am to 9pm.
.
🍜 Tonkotsu Ramen ($16.47)
🍜 Gyu Don ($16.47)
🍜 Gyoza ($6.84)
.
Current promotion:
▪️Free Delivery from now till 4th May 2020
▪️Free Gyoza with min $80.00. Valid for Pickup and Delivery.
.
#kanadayasg #sgramen #burpple #burpplesg #stayhome #supportlocalfnb #savefnbsg #circuitbreakersg #circuitbreakerextended
